# 🌐 Special Space Train — Universal App Server

> “This is not just a server. It's a **launchpad** for everything that will matter in your next-gen apps, Create your own api ai auto-assign.yml ” 🚀

## 🎯 Project Goal

Special Space Train is a **Web Server Infrastructure** designed to be **Central Hub** between mobile apps (iOS & Android) and cloud databases

📱 Supports:
- Mobile apps (both iOS and Android)
- REST API / WebSocket
- Large-scale databases
- Login, user management, token-based auth

🎮 Compatible with:
- Game apps
- Slots/casino systems
- Business apps/data collection forms
- Real-time databases
- The unwritten but dreamed-for future ✨

---

## ⚙️ Technologies used

| Stack | Details |
|------|-------------|
| `Node.js` | Server core |
| `Express.js` | Routing API and Middleware |
| `MongoDB` / `PostgreSQL` | Scalable data storage |
| `JWT` | Authentication system (Authentication) |
| Docker | For container deployment |
| Socket.IO | Real-time API |
| CORS + HTTPS | Secure and mobile app-friendly |

